Company Overview of Smart Portfolios, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Smart Portfolios, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, corporations, charitable institutions, and sovereign nations. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It employs a combination of quantitative and fundamental analysis with a bottom-up approach to make its investments. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against a composite index comprising 35% of Russell 3000 Index, 35% of MSCI Index ex U.S. Index, and 30% of Barclays Aggregate Bond Index. Smart Portfolios, LLC is bas...
Smart Portfolios, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, corporations, charitable institutions, and sovereign nations. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It employs a combination of quantitative and fundamental analysis with a bottom-up approach to make its investments. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against a composite index comprising 35% of Russell 3000 Index, 35% of MSCI Index ex U.S. Index, and 30% of Barclays Aggregate Bond Index. Smart Portfolios, LLC is based in Seattle, Washington.
