How do I update this listing?




                                             Smart Portfolios is based out of Seattle. Smart Portfolios is a large advisory firm with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $152,584,627 (Form ADV from 2017-03-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q2 2017 included $92,902,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 82.71%. Smart Portfolios's largest holding is iShares Floating Rate Bond with shares held of 450,098.  Smart Portfolios has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 29 13F filings in our database for Smart Portfolios. 
                                           






